# 2015-04-04
* added oneshot functionality to ensure pipe is only written to once

# 2013-02-12
* added inotify event watching via [pyinotify](http://pyinotify.sourceforge.net/) to track when other end of pipe is closes
* removed unnecessary block and interval options
* fixed bug in mode option
* added FIFO checks to avoid problems in unexpected events such FIFO deletion while running
